divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: Today, Saturday the 19th at around 6:10 P.M. It was slightly cloudy. I was sitting in my backyard playing my Mario brothers on Gameboy when I look up and see some lights in the sky. At first I think plane but as I looked more at them they didn t really fit the pattern of a plane, This circular kinda thing that stood out against the clouds had lights on each end. A white one on two sides and on the other two sides it had four lights, they kept changing colors which really made me doubt it was a plane. I just watched for a little while until it disappeared into the horizon.
